# Hugging Face access token — required for speaker diarization.
# 1. Create a free token (Read scope): https://huggingface.co/settings/tokens
# 2. Accept the license for this gated model while logged in:
#    https://huggingface.co/pyannote/speaker-diarization-community-1
# Without this token the app still transcribes, but speaker labels are disabled.
HF_TOKEN=hf_your_token_here
